pullRequest.title: SAK-44376 Changed the messaging and the default size of Samigo's File Upload question type
pullRequest.bodyText:
https://jira.sakaiproject.org/browse/SAK-44376
For the File Upload question type, I:

changed the default of "samigo.sizeMax" to "20480" for 20MB to match "content.upload.max" because the "samigo.sizeMax" property has to be less than or equal to "content.upload.max"  - this change also updates the max size in the user-facing message
updated the documentation of the default in default.sakai.properties
added comments to "samigo.sizeMax" in default.sakai.properties to mention that it has to be lower than or equal to "content.upload.max"
updated the message to be less specific about the browser-controlled button label using my suggested message from above
fixed a banner on the related Remove File page

commit.message: SAK-44376 Changed the messaging and the default size of Samigo's upload question type

nodes.bodyText: If these strings aren't translated in their respective languages, you can just remove them from the files. It will fall back to the default language anyway. Having these keys in the other language files may make it seem like they're already translated, and then they won't ever get translated.
